{
  "url": "https://www.hymnal.net/cn/hymn/ch/466",
  "title": "若是死了哦这是主",
  "verses": [
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "『若 是"
            },
            {
              "chord": "Bm",
              "text": "死 了！』"
            },
            {
              "chord": "Em",
              "text": "哦， 这"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "A7",
              "text": "是 主"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "亲 口"
            },
            {
              "chord": "A7",
              "text": "的 信"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "息！ 『若"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "是"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "B7",
              "text": "死 了，"
            },
            {
              "chord": "Em",
              "text": "就 必"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "结"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "出"
            },
            {
              "chord": "A7",
              "text": "许 多"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "的 子"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "粒。』"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "1"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "人得生命，你若真要，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "你就必须死；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "落在地里死了，葬了，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "就必能结实。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "但主不会死中留你，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "祂命必逞能；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "祂必使你从死复起，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "充满了新生。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "你愿走主生命道路，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "释放祂生命？"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "当你经过死的路途，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "生命才供应。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "你要学这有福秘诀："
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "不死就不生；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "倒出生命，直到死绝，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "收获必丰盈。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    }
  ],
  "metadata": {
    "category": "十字架的道路",
    "time": "6/4",
    "hymn_code": "3721413217555",
    "related": [
      {
        "url": "https://www.hymnal.net/cn/hymn/h/636",
        "language": "cn",
        "category": "h",
        "number": "636",
        "title": "E636"
      }
    ]
  },
  "raw_sections": [
    "『若 是死 了！』哦， 这",
    "是 主亲 口的 信息！ 『若是",
    "死 了，就 必结",
    "出许 多的 子粒。』",
    "人得生命，你若真要，",
    "你就必须死；",
    "落在地里死了，葬了，",
    "就必能结实。",
    "但主不会死中留你，",
    "祂命必逞能；",
    "祂必使你从死复起，",
    "充满了新生。",
    "你愿走主生命道路，",
    "释放祂生命？",
    "当你经过死的路途，",
    "生命才供应。",
    "你要学这有福秘诀：",
    "不死就不生；",
    "倒出生命，直到死绝，",
    "收获必丰盈。"
  ]
}